  "title": "Skip Sleep",
  "description": "Sets Minecraft player sleep percentage",
  "body": "# What is this datapack/mod about?\n> This datapack/mod sets your sleepPercentage to 0, so only 1 player needed to sleep and skip the night!\n\n## What are the options?\n> The options are 100 (reset), 50, 10 and 0\n\n## How to use?\n> Use these commands:\n> Set 0 (Skip the night): /function setsleep0\n> Set 10: /function setsleep10\n> Set 50: /function setsleep50\n> Reset: /function resetsleep",
